OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly fog will clear in the
OL,6,Feast and low cloud with patchy drizzle
OL,7,Fwill become confined to eastern
OL,8,FScotland and northeast England.
OL,9,FOtherwise mostly dry and settled with
OL,10,Flight winds and some very warm
OL,11,Fsunshine. Isolated showers affecting
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FLow cloud across the
OL,15,Fnortheast will become more extensive
OL,16,Facross eastern and some central parts
OL,17,Fof the UK overnight. Patchy rain
OL,18,Fdeveloping across western Scotland.
OL,19,FDry with clear spells elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
